<emphasis italics="true" pageId="92" pageNumber="93">Agriophyllum tibeticum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Sukhor. sp. nov. (BM001209885).
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph pageId="92" pageNumber="93">Eight species (including a new species described below) distributed in Irano-Turanian region (7 spp.) and Tibet (1 sp.).</paragraph>
